    <p style="margin: 0; max-width: unset;">This is a current work in progress page. I am using a modified version <a href="https://github.com/xdesro/posse-with-11ty"  target="_blank">Henry Desroches' Posse with 11ty repo</a> to be able to post content from <a href="https://quill.p3k.io" target="_blank">quill.p3k.io</a> save to the <a href="https://github.com/bigandy/11ty-site" target="_blank">github.com/bigandy/11ty-site github repository</a> and then publish here.</p>
